:4:\"data\";s:19:\"affiliate marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"adding affiliate links in WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=155556\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:645:\"<p>Wondering how to add affiliate links in WordPress? If you&#8217;ve got a blog with a decent number of daily visitors, you can earn plenty of referral income with affiliate marketing; but you have to be smart when choosing the tools to turn your blog into a successful affiliate marketing site. In this article, we’ll show [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-affiliate-links-in-wordpress-and-properly-track-them/\">How to Add Affiliate Links in WordPress (and Properly Track Them)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16053:\"<p>Wondering how to add affiliate links in WordPress? If you&#8217;ve got a blog with a decent number of daily visitors, you can earn plenty of referral income with affiliate marketing; but you have to be smart when choosing the tools to turn your blog into a successful affiliate marketing site.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to add and organize affiliate links in WordPress using ThirstyAffiliates. Then, in the last section of the article, we’ll show how to properly track your affiliate links to grow your affiliate marketing.</p>\n<h3>Using ThirstyAffiliates to Add and Organize Affiliate Links in WordPress</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ThirstyAffiliates</a> is the best affiliate management and cloaking plugin for WordPress. It helps you to cloak your affiliate links and add them into your blog posts with ease. You can also organize your affiliate links by categories and add automatic keywords so that affiliate management in WordPress will be really easy.</p>\n<p>In general, affiliate links are long and look ugly that are hard to remember. Most affiliate links look like this:</p>\n<p>http://example.com/products/?product_id=123&#038;affiliate_id</p>\n<p>ThirstyAffiliates helps you to cloak such affiliate links to make them short and branded URLs as shown below:</p>\n<p>http://www.yoursite.com/recommends/productname</p>\n<p>As you grow as an affiliate marketer, you’re likely to use the same affiliate link on tons of different blog posts. With ThirstyAffiliates, you can store all your affiliate links in one place in your WordPress backend and use them whenever you need. Plus, it has a fully functional search option to help you search for links by the link title.</p>\n<p>In addition to proper management of affiliate links, cloaking also helps you to prevent commission theft. By using cloaked links, you can add an additional layer of click tracking to ensure you are getting paid for every sale you refer.</p>\n<p>Now, let’s go ahead and see how to add affiliate links in WordPress step-by-step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install ThirstyAffiliates and Configure Settings</h3>\n<p>First of all, go to the <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ThirstyAffiliates</a> website and buy a subscription plan. Then, go ahead and install the plugin in WordPress.</p>\n<p>After the plugin is activated on your site, go to <strong>ThirstyAffiliates » Settings</strong> from your WordPress dashboard. This will open the <strong>General</strong> tab in ThirstyAffiliate Settings.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155953\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-general-settings.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-general-settings\" width=\"560\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-general-settings.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-general-settings-300x155.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you can review all the settings and change the settings if you want to. At the end, don’t forget to click the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n<p>Second tab in ThirstyAffiliates settings is <strong>Link Appearance</strong>. It allows you to configure settings that affect the behavior and appearance or your affiliate links. You can configure some of the important settings from there.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155954\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings\" width=\"560\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>First, you can choose a link prefix that will be used in your cloaked links before your affiliate ID. The plugin, by default, has <strong>/recommends/</strong> set up which you can replace with any of the available prefixes such as recommends, fly, proceed, goto, etc. Also, you can choose <strong>custom</strong> to add a new prefix.</p>\n<p>Next, you can choose whether you want to show a link category in your affiliate URL or not. Then, you can choose link redirect type, use no follow on links, and open links in new window.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155955\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings-2.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings-2\" width=\"560\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings-2.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-appearance-settings-2-300x273.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Review all the settings, make the necessary changes, and then, click <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n<p>The third tab in ThirstAffiliates Settings is <strong>Modules</strong>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155956\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-module-settings.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-module-settings\" width=\"560\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-module-settings.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-module-settings-300x226.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>From this page, you can enable ThirstyAffiliates statistics that collects data about your users who click your affiliate links. If it&#8217;s enabled, it shows reports; however, the module slows down your site. So we recommend using <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> for tracking your affiliate links.</p>\n<p>The <strong>Link Fixer</strong> will help you to fix any outdated / broken affiliate links on your site. <strong>Uncloak Links</strong> will allow you to uncloak specific links or categories to make it compatible with some affiliate programs with stricter terms (such as Amazon Associates).</p>\n<p>The fourth tab <strong>Import/Export</strong> provides you with options to export ThirstyAffiliates settings and import settings from other WordPress sites.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155957\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-import-export-settings.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-import-export-settings\" width=\"560\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-import-export-settings.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-import-export-settings-300x241.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>After you choose the options, make sure to click the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Add Link Categories and New Affiliate Links</h3>\n<p>After you’ve configured the settings, you’re now ready to create link categories.</p>\n<p>To add link categories, go to <strong>ThirstyAffiliates » Link Categories</strong> from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155958\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-categories.jpg\" alt=\"thirstyaffiliates-link-categories\" width=\"560\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-categories.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/thirstyaffiliates-link-categories-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, give a name to your new link category, set a slug, and add a description. Then, click the <strong>Add New Category</strong> button.</p>\n<p>After you create sufficient categories for your links, you can go ahead and add your links.</p>\n<p>To add a new affiliate link, you’ll need to go to <strong>ThirstyAffiliates » New Affiliate Link</strong> from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p>Now, you can easily add affiliate links.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155959\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates.jpg\" alt=\"add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates\" width=\"560\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates-300x174.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>In the first field, give a name to your link. You can use the product’s name so that it’ll be easy to search and embed in posts.</p>\n<p>Next, you’ll need to add the original affiliate link in the <strong>Destination URL</strong> field.</p>\n<p>Then, you can attach images as well. This is useful for website owners who want to display affiliate links with images in sidebars. You can also add autolink keywords for your affiliate link if you’re using ThirstyAffiliates&#8217; paid version.</p>\n<p>In the right panel, you can choose a link category. As you scroll down, you can find link options. You’ll see the options as you configured in the <strong>Link Appearance</strong> as we discussed above. Review them, and click the <strong>Save Link</strong> button.</p>\n<p>That’s it. Now, you can repeat the same process to add more affiliate links.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Adding Affiliate Links in WordPress Posts and Pages</h3>\n<p>Once you’ve added affiliate links in <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ThirstyAffiliates</a>, now you can add the cloaked affiliate links in your posts and pages.</p>\n<p>ThirstyAffiliates makes the process of adding links really easy as it adds an icon in your post editor to embed affiliate links.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155960\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/embed-affiliate-link-in-post.jpg\" alt=\"embed-affiliate-link-in-post\" width=\"560\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/embed-affiliate-link-in-post.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/embed-affiliate-link-in-post-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>As you click on the link, it’ll open the search box where you can type your affiliate link name. Then, you can select and add on your post.</p>\n<p>It also has another icon, <strong>Quick Add Affiliate Link</strong>, that you can use to add a new affiliate link and embed it in your post.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155961\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-icon.jpg\" alt=\"quck-add-affiliate-link-icon\" width=\"560\" height=\"195\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-icon.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-icon-300x104.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>When you click on the icon, a popup box will appear. You can add a new affiliate link and then embed it in the post.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155962\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates.jpg\" alt=\"quck-add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates\" width=\"560\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/quck-add-affiliate-link-thirstyaffiliates-300x161.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>That’s it. Now, you can publish your post and check if your affiliate links are working.</p>\n<h3>How to Properly Track Your Affiliate Links</h3>\n<p>ThirstyAffilites comes with a Statistics module that tracks the affiliate clicks on your site; however, it’ll slow down your website because it uses your website&#8217;s resources.</p>\n<p>So, we recommend you use <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> to track your affiliate links. Since it uses event-based tracking from Google Analytics, it won’t affect your website speed. Plus, the reports from Google Analytics are more reliable than any other services.</p>\n<p>Now, let’s see how to enable affiliate tracking in WordPress using MonsterInsights.</p>\n<h3>Affiliate Links Tracking with MonsterInsights</h3>\n<p>MonsterInsights makes affiliate links tracking for ThirstAffiliates fully automatic and effortless. Now you don&#8217;t need to do a single thing to set up affiliate tracking in WordPress. </p>\n<p>When the MonsterInsights plugin is installed on your site, it&#8217;ll automatically detect if you&#8217;re using ThirstyAffiliates and track all your affiliate links. Use any prefix (/refer/, /recommends/ or /out/), the plugin will do its job. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/affiliate-link-tracking.png\" alt=\"Affiliate Link Tracking with MonsterInsights\" width=\"620\" height=\"292\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179067\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/affiliate-link-tracking.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/affiliate-link-tracking-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The automatic affiliate tracking feature empowers anyone to manage affiliate tracking without having to hire a developer. Also, you can save plenty of time and reduce all the possible setup errors.  </p>\n<p>Best of all, you can view your affiliate tracking reports right in your WordPress dashboard. Just visit <strong> Insights » Reports » Publishers</strong> from your admin panel to view the reports.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155898\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/affiliate-link-tracking-report-monsterinsights.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-link-tracking-report-monsterinsights\" width=\"560\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/affiliate-link-tracking-report-monsterinsights.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/affiliate-link-tracking-report-monsterinsights-280x300.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>You can always click the <strong>View All Affiliate Links Report</strong> to view more reports in Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>If you want detailed instructions, here’s our complete guide on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-set-up-affiliate-link-tracking-in-wordpress/\">setting up affiliate links tracking</a>.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to learn how to add affiliate links in WordPress and to properly track them.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-check-the-number-of-visitors-for-your-wordpress-site/\">how to check the number of visitors for your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more Google Analytics tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-affiliate-links-in-wordpress-and-properly-track-them/\">How to Add Affiliate Links in WordPress (and Properly Track Them)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:101:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-affiliate-links-in-wordpress-and-properly-track-them/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:37:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:10:{s:6:\"server\";s:12:\"nginx/1.15.7\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Fri, 24 May 2019 07:44:01 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:10:\"set-cookie\";s:98:\"srv_id=64fd515db0370e752ab9384b7787d180; expires=Fri, 24-May-19 08:44:01 GMT; max-age=3600; path=/\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Thu, 23 May 2019 18:41:08 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"dddf9351714e66f09f79397dd87b8442\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:4:\"link\";s:68:\"<https://www.m