ress site? A coming soon page is a great way to create hype about the launch of your product or service and even built an email list before launching your website. And with the help of a WordPress theme or plugin, you [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-coming-soon-plugins-and-themes/\">9 Best WordPress Coming Soon Plugins and Themes (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Sandipan Mukherjee\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18087:\"<p>Are you looking for the best coming soon plugin or theme for your WordPress site? A coming soon page is a great way to create hype about the launch of your product or service and even built an email list before launching your website. And with the help of a WordPress theme or plugin, you can add a coming soon page to your site without much hassle.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress coming soon plugins and themes in 2019.</p>\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SeedProd</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-459419 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-plugin.png\" alt=\"SeedProd plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-plugin-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SeedProd is the best maintenance mode and coming soon plugin for WordPress. You can easily build beautiful coming soon page for your site using this plugin.</p>\n<p>It lets you add a countdown timer to your site so that your visitors can know exactly when your site is getting live. You may also add a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-popup-in-wordpress/\">popup contact form</a> to allow people to get in touch with you.</p>\n<p>Want to build your email list before launching your site? You can easily do that by integrating this plugin with <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-email-marketing-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">popular email marketing services</a> including <a title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact</a>, <a  title=\"Drip\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/drip/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" >Drip</a>, and <a title=\"ConvertKit\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/convertkit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ConvertKit</a>.</p>\n<p>SeedProd comes with over 50 elegantly designed templates to choose from. Thus, you can select a template of your choice and make the necessary changes quickly without having to build anything from scratch.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459455\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-template.jpg\" alt=\"seedprod template\" width=\"562\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-template.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/seedprod-template-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>It also offers a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-drag-and-drop-wordpress-page-builders/\">powerful page builder</a> that allows you to change fonts, colors, layout, section, animations, and much more. And the best part is you can see all the changes in real time. Isn&#8217;t that cool?</p>\n<p>Anyways, some of the other features of SeedProd are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;s responsive and retina ready.</li>\n<li>Offers more than 750 Google Fonts.</li>\n<li>Hide or show parts of your site based on the user role and IP address.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-create-gdpr-compliant-forms/\">Compliant with GDPR</a> (General Data Protection Regulation).</li>\n<li>Get access to 500,000+ free background images.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Last but not least, it comes with a social sharing and referral tracking system that allows you to offer incentives to people for sharing your site on popular social networks like Facebook, Twitter, and Pinterest. Thus, you can make your site viral even before the official launch.</p>\n<p>Overall, SeedProd is the best coming soon WordPress plugin in the market with tons of useful feature. So <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">get started with SeedProd today</a>!</p>\n<h3>2. <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-436650\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/divi-builder-plugin.png\" alt=\"Divi Builder Plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/divi-builder-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/divi-builder-plugin-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Divi is one of the best WordPress page builder plugins in the market. It&#8217;s a drag and drop builder that lets you create beautiful pages including a coming soon page for your website.</p>\n<p>It comes with 46 content modules including buttons, countdown timer, video slider, email optin, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-testimonials-from-wordpress-form-submissions/\">testimonial</a>, and contact form to make your life easy.</p>\n<p>So you can use a blank page template and various content modules to build the coming soon page as per your requirement. You can also customize every part of your page and see the changes live.</p>\n<p>Don&#8217;t want to build it from scratch? Elegant Themes, the team behind the Divi plugin, also offers <a href=\"https://www.elegantthemes.com/blog/divi-resources/download-the-free-divi-coming-soon-pages-layout-kit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">8 coming soon page layouts for free</a>. You can import the one you like and make changes to the layout using the Divi builder.</p>\n<h3>3. <a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"OceanWP\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459418\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-theme-coming-soon-demo.png\" alt=\"OceanWP theme coming soon demo\" width=\"562\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-theme-coming-soon-demo.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-theme-coming-soon-demo-300x160.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OceanWP is a lightweight, responsive, and multipurpose WordPress theme. And with 300,000+ active installs, it&#8217;s one of the most popular themes in the WordPress theme directory.</p>\n<p>This theme comes with more than 70 demos to choose from, including <a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/demo-category/coming-soon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5 coming soon demo templates</a>. And you can import the demo content, widgets, and customizer settings to get started quickly.</p>\n<p>OceanWP provides a number of extensions like cookie notice, popup login, and social sharing to enhance its functionality. It&#8217;s also compatible with some of the best drag and drop page builders including <a title=\"Elementor Pro\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Elementor</a>, <a title=\"Divi\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Divi</a>, <a title=\"Beaver Builder\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Beaver Builder</a>, and <a title=\"Visual Composer\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/visual-composer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Visual Composer</a>.</p>\n<p>This theme is a translation and RTL (right to left) ready theme. So you can easily <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/guides/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">start your website</a> in any language of your choice or even in multiple languages.</p>\n<h3>4. <a title=\"Themify Landing\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Landing</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Themify Landing\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459420\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify-landing-wordpress-theme.png\" alt=\"Themify Landing WordPress Theme\" width=\"562\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify-landing-wordpress-theme.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify-landing-wordpress-theme-300x175.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Landing is a premium WordPress theme for building landing pages. It comes with Themify&#8217;s page builder and thus, helps you to design the pages of your site using its drag and drop interface.</p>\n<p>This theme provides various header design options like choose a background type, select header text color, hide certain elements, and more.</p>\n<p>It also offers more than 25 pre-built landing page templates. And just like OceanWP theme, it includes a coming soon template to make life easy for you.</p>\n<p>Landing theme allows you to quickly upload your logo and add social icons to your coming soon page. You can also add a countdown timer, a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-simple-contact-form-in-wordpress/\">simple contact form</a>, and a subscription box to <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">build your email list</a> using MailChimp integration.</p>\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/cmp-coming-soon-maintenance/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">CMP – Coming Soon &amp; Maintenance Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/cmp-coming-soon-maintenance/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459414\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cmp-coming-soon-and-maintenance-plugin.png\" alt=\"CMP coming soon and maintenance plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cmp-coming-soon-and-maintenance-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cmp-coming-soon-and-maintenance-plugin-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CMP is a free coming soon and maintenance mode WordPress plugin.</p>\n<p>It works perfectly on any device and is also compatible with every WordPress theme. You can easily activate the coming soon or under construction pages with a single click.</p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the features of this plugin:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use video, image, slider, patterns, color gradients, or solid colors as background.</li>\n<li>Display social media icons on your site.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Insert Google Analytics code to track your site traffic</a>.</li>\n<li>Offers custom subscription form to collect emails.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Apart from the above features, this plugin allows you to enable CMP only on specific pages. You can also generate a bypass URL so that some of your users can see the under construction site.</p>\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/minimal-coming-soon-maintenance-mode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Minimal Coming Soon &amp; Maintenance Mode</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459416\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/minimal-coming-soon-and-maintenance-mode-plugin.png\" alt=\"Minimal coming soon and maintenance mode plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/minimal-coming-soon-and-maintenance-mode-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/minimal-coming-soon-and-maintenance-mode-plugin-300x133.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>Minimal Coming Soon and Maintenance Mode is a freemium plugin using which you can quickly configure a coming soon or launch page without any hassle.</p>\n<p>Want to customize your site? You can modify every part of your website including background, cover image, logo, and fonts. You can even <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-style-wpforms-with-custom-css-beginners-guide/\">add custom CSS code</a> if you&#8217;re good at CSS.</p>\n<p>Just like most plugins on our list, you can add a subscription box to your page and connect it to <a title=\"AWeber\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/aweber-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AWeber</a> or <a title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact</a> to collect leads.</p>\n<p>This plugin also has a pro version that provides 90+ templates, 26 background image filters, and 47 content animations to take your coming soon page to the next level.</p>\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-maintenance-mode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WP Maintenance Mode</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-maintenance-mode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459422\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wp-maintenance-mode-plugin.png\" alt=\"WP Maintenance Mode Plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wp-maintenance-mode-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wp-maintenance-mode-plugin-300x133.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Maintenance Mode is another free coming soon plugin on our list. You can use it to add a coming soon page as well as a maintenance mode page.</p>\n<p>This plugin lets you add a countdown timer, subscription form, and a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-responsive-contact-form-with-multiple-columns/\">simple contact form</a> to your page. And you can customize the colors, text, and background using the visual customizer.</p>\n<p>WP Maintenance Mode is compatible with almost every WordPress theme. This GDPR-ready plugin can also be used on WordPress multisite installs and provides maintenance settings to each blog from the network.</p>\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/nifty-coming-soon-and-under-construction-page/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nifty</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/nifty-coming-soon-and-under-construction-page/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459417\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/nifty-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"Nifty WordPress plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/nifty-wordpress-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/nifty-wordpress-plugin-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Nifty is a simple and easy-to-use coming soon and under construction plugin. It allows you to set up responsive pages and thus, your site will load perfectly on every device.</p>\n<p>Some of the important features of this plugin are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Comes with 300+ Google Fonts.</li>\n<li>Use slider or solid colors as background.</li>\n<li>Option to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-mailchimp-subscribe-form-in-wordpress/\">add MailChimp subscription form</a>.</li>\n<li>Countdown timer included.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Do you want to preview your coming soon page without using another web browser? This plugin lets you do that with the help of the live preview feature. Cool, isn&#8217;t it?</p>\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/igniteup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">IgniteUp</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/igniteup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-459415\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/igniteup-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"IgniteUp WordPress plugin\" width=\"562\" height=\"178\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/igniteup-wordpress-plugin.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/igniteup-wordpress-plugin-300x95.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></a></p>\n<p>IgniteUp is a free coming soon plugin that comes with 7 templates to choose from. You can easily customize a template to set up your page within a few minutes.</p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can show your under construction website to specific users by sharing a secret URL or by whitelisting their IP addresses.</p>\n<p>This plugin also allows you to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-custom-mailerlite-signup-form-in-wordpress/\">add a subscription form</a> to your site and integrate your form to MailChimp and MailPoet. And later, you can access the email subscriber list by <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-export-wordpress-form-entries-to-csv/\">exporting it as CSV</a>.</p>\n<h3>Final Thoughts</h3>\n<p>After comparing the features of the above themes and plugins, we can conclude that <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SeedProd</a> is a step ahead of all its competitors.</p>\n<p>It comes with tons of useful features, offers 50+ templates, and allows you to customize your coming soon page as per your requirements. And the best part is you don&#8217;t need any coding knowledge.</p>\n<p>Anyways, we hope this article helped you to find the best coming soon plugin or theme for your site.</p>\n<p>Looking for the best managed WordPress hosting service for your website? Check out our comparison article on the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-managed-wordpress-hosting/\">best managed WordPress hosting companies in 2019</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, follow us on <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-coming-soon-plugins-and-themes/\">9 Best WordPress Coming Soon Plugins and Themes (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://wpforms.com/best-wordpress-coming-soon-plugins-and-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"d